#   		window tagging
#   
#   %pause
#   	Also...
#   		menu bar with status widgets
#   		plug-in support
#   		plan9 filesystem for configuration
#   		fully scriptable
#   		small codebase, small footprint, low overhead
#   
#   %% codebase 10k lines
#   %% footprint 15M + 30M ruby
#   %% overhead 20-30 pixels vertically, 2 pixels horizontally
#   
#   %right
